{"id":396933988,"lang":"python3","lang_name":"Python3","time":"2 years, 11 months","timestamp":1600325954,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"144 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/396933988/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"14 MB","code":"class Solution:\n    def lengthOfLongestSubstring(self, s: str) -> int:\n        m = {}\n        ans, i = 0, 0\n        # \"abba\"\n        for j in range(len(s)):\n            if s[j] in m:\n                # 确保i至少是j的下一个元素，太巧妙\n                i = max(i, m.get(s[j])+1)\n            m[s[j]] = j\n            ans = max(ans, j-i+1)\n        return ans","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
